ank\": 1.9214120931481504e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 3009, \"end\": 3012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajoran\", \"score\": 0.9999560142015721, \"rank\": 4.392950389844346e-05, \"text\": \"Kai\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajoran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajoran\"}, {\"begin\": 3057, \"end\": 3067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakakibara_clan\", \"score\": 0.9999999999731699, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sakakibara\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakakibara_clan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakakibara_clan\"}, {\"begin\": 3089, \"end\": 3092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajoran\", \"score\": 0.9999560142015721, \"rank\": 4.392950389844346e-05, \"text\": \"Kai\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajoran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajoran\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"concussion\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2861}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2875}, {\"ngram\": \"that emotional rollercoaster\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2907}, {\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2943}, {\"ngram\": \"the emotions\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 2991}, {\"ngram\": \"her brother\", \"from\": 3076, \"to\": 3087}, {\"ngram\": \"a promising BMX racer\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3115}, {\"ngram\": \"a severe brain injury\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Eleven months later, after that concussion, I had another concussion, and fearing the sport a lot.\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3274, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that concussion\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3218}, {\"ngram\": \"another concussion\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3244}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3258, \"to\": 3267}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was not enjoying it, and after the concussion, I thought it was the end for me and not worth the risk of having another concussion.\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the concussion\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3322}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 3341, \"to\": 3348}, {\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3378}, {\"ngram\": \"another concussion\", \"from\": 3389, \"to\": 3407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Head injuries are so scary, and having gone through two back-to-back, I did not think it was something that I could push through.\", \"from\": 3409, \"to\": 3538, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Head injuries\", \"from\": 3409, \"to\": 3422}, {\"ngram\": \"back\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3477}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Before Tokyo and that crash, I was doing pretty good, and there was that burning desire for what could have been.\", \"from\": 3540, \"to\": 3654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3548, \"end\": 3553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999980410735676, \"rank\": 1.9214120931481504e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that crash\", \"from\": 3558, \"to\": 3568}, {\"ngram\": \"that burning desire\", \"from\": 3609, \"to\": 3628}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew that if I had given it all up, I would have been disappointed in myself that I did not give it another crack.\", \"from\": 3655, \"to\": 3771, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another crack\", \"from\": 3757, \"to\": 3770}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With those experiences, I went through drastic changes in my life, and needed to find that relationship with BMX.\", \"from\": 3773, \"to\": 3887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3883, \"end\": 3886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX_racing\", \"score\": 0.6813913408908717, \"rank\": 0.4675854241010598, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX_racing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX_racing\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those experiences\", \"from\": 3779, \"to\": 3796}, {\"ngram\": \"drastic changes\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3828}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 3832, \"to\": 3839}, {\"ngram\": \"that relationship\", \"from\": 3860, \"to\": 3877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was able to find myself as a racer because up until that point I was a racer with Kai, and I had to find myself as a racer without Kai by my side.\\\"\", \"from\": 3888, \"to\": 4037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3972, \"end\": 3975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajoran\", \"score\": 0.9999560142015721, \"rank\": 4.392950389844346e-05, \"text\": \"Kai\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajoran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajoran\"}, {\"begin\": 4021, \"end\": 4024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajoran\", \"score\": 0.9999560142015721, \"rank\": 4.392950389844346e-05, \"text\": \"Kai\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajoran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajoran\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a racer\", \"from\": 3917, \"to\": 3924}, {\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 3942, \"to\": 3952}, {\"ngram\": \"a racer\", \"from\": 3959, \"to\": 3966}, {\"ngram\": \"a racer\", \"from\": 4005, \"to\": 4012}, {\"ngram\": \"my side\", \"from\": 4028, \"to\": 4035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The rider who still races with the number 77, to represent her brother on the track, dedicated the gold medal to him.\", \"from\": 4039, \"to\": 4156, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The rider\", \"from\": 4039, \"to\": 4048}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 4070, \"to\": 4080}, {\"ngram\": \"her brother\", \"from\": 4098